{"tid":472071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳嘉倩心口仔紅色一撻撻","createTime":"2017-11-18T00:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T03:56:10.000Z","uid":3806,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"261f22d6ff12e25d042f1e91623e8cb3961e5ca6","tid":472071,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171114092435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171114092435&h=e8f2c970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前新聞主播陳嘉倩到觀塘，為健康食品宣傳，見她心口仔紅色一撻撻，點解呢可？受訪時，她指自己今次拍廣告是比較新的嘗試：「自己都喺度適應當中。（廣告酬勞比做主播好得多？）一份係freelance工作，一份係full time工作，都冇得咁樣比較嘅！（想唔想拍戲或者拍電視劇？）未有人搵，但最緊要睇劇本同角色，適合自己咪試吓，我唔抗拒！」<br />\n<br />\n問到嘉倩BB，事業得意，愛情是否亦多姿多彩？她說：「發展緊，了解當中，從來都冇多姿多彩。（係咪同過一位叫Wilson嘅醫生拍拖？）係之前嘅事。（話你一腳踏兩船？）唔知點解有呢啲傳聞，但每個人都有以前嘅事，依家專注工作同學業方面。（依家只得一段感情？）梗係啦！（有指你發展中呢位男士有位嫩模女友？）冇聽過，應該唔會有，了解緊，感情事希望低調處理，想大家集中番喺我工作。（話你收『兵』？）我冇當任何人係『兵』，都係正常朋友，社交圈子有男有女。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_02b.jpg?20171114092435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20171114092435&h=5c0835fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉倩BB心口仔現紅色一撻撻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_03b.jpg?20171114092435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20171114092435&h=dd2d50da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家想唔想睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171114092435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171114092435&h=ec3567ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉倩BB晒腿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_05b.jpg?20171114092435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20171114092435&h=6d10028a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉倩BB又話自己唔收兵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171113%2Fbkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001.html&d=Fy44ZujKm9oT4Thc8K%2FcJXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3ef3fc0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171113/bkn-20171113230618997-1113_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d4adc73de5dec6a971bc241387352573a7a1b7d","tid":472071,"uid":57835,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"濃妝寶"},{"pid":"fc8ca2ffe945cbd71666897fd6538f00118d2d23","tid":472071,"uid":953,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"唔係主播look 即刻好樣衰"},{"pid":"014b6e0aabb344f99de6919f0ca0de95c6391d41","tid":472071,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"還我馬尾look"},{"pid":"4964fa3d5a0e49a64e00a9ce5cea3d582a541d5c","tid":472071,"uid":56230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"對腳粗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563f5731f86559c33491967aae4644dd404879e6","tid":472071,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:0